### Ticketing & Seat Locking Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@userToken = YOUR_USER_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 1. [PUBLIC] Browse Events to get ID and Tier ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

### 2. [USER] Reserve Tickets (Short-lived lock)
# Use eventId and tierId from Request #1
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/reserve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "eventId": 1,
    "tierId": 1,
    "quantity": 2
}

### 3. [USER] Confirm Purchase (Simulate Payment)
# In real flow, this follows payment gateway redirect
POST {{baseUrl}}/tickets/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "eventId": 1,
    "tierId": 1,
    "quantity": 2
}

### 4. [USER] View My Tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 5. [ADMIN/SYSTEM] Mock QR Scan (Use Ticket ID from Request #4)
# In production, this is called by the scanner app
# Note: No route for this yet, test via service later or add here if needed.
